Current date can be put in by adding ${DATE:yyyy} where yyyy can be replaced be the same syntax as defined in the class java.text.SimpleDateFormat. Other fields are:


${WORKERID}

${WORKERNAME}

${REMOTEIP}

${REQUESTID}

${TRANSACTIONID}

${USERNAME}

